{"tid":1187113,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"福田雄一執導2020日本電影「新解釋・三國志」","createTime":"2019-06-05T11:56:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T12:38:20.000Z","uid":38631,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"953c7bf02d9f6279dcf683cbda4185684a285916","tid":1187113,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T11:56:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/05/tXfeMI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2FtXfeMI.png&h=d0bda8fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福田雄一執導2020日本電影「新解釋・三國志」<br />\n這次要挑戰改編歷史名著！<br />\n<br />\n以福田雄一導演撰寫的原創劇本製作的電影「新解釋・三國志」，由大泉洋擔綱主演，飾演武將．劉備玄德，電影造型也首度曝光，這也是大泉洋與福田雄一的首次合作<br />\n<br />\n不知道福田導演會把《三國志》改編成什麼樣的故事？劇情跟卡司都很讓人期待啊～<br />\n<br />\n電影目前已經開拍，預計2020年上映<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xa5yRWNj4uk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxa5yRWNj4uk&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElpwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=eb1058f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xa5yRWNj4uk</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/05/rTOY0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F05%2FrTOY0b.png&h=5fbcb3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劉備．大泉洋"},{"pid":"22a3900d1301bb40c638062642b472d71d242d51","tid":1187113,"uid":38631,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T12:01:02.000Z","msg":"一定有<br />\n<br />\n橋本環奈、佐藤二朗、山崎賢人、新井浩文、賀來賢人、吉澤亮、山田孝之<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449d4020e7c90b7ca1304571fee07d00ac342c6b","tid":1187113,"uid":112316,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"日本仔咪撚再搞三國啦<br />\n次次都死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas